  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of the research is to create a tool that can make a good diagnosis of&#xD;
      cognitive abilities in Alzheimer's patients. As a secondary objective, the investigators&#xD;
      intend to examine both the percentage of correct answers and the response times and see their&#xD;
      relationship with age, gender, sex, months since the onset of the disease and years of&#xD;
      training.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
